U.K. stocks rose, reversing
declines. The benchmark FTSE 100 climbed 15.66, or 0.3 percent,
to 5,719.43 as of 3:07 p.m. in  London , having earlier fallen as
much as 0.7 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
